Meet Taco, #A5142014,a sweet, 2 year old chihuahua mix with amazingly expressive ears. Not much is know about this precious little guy since he just arrived as a transfer. We do know that he is scared of the loud noises at the shelter; he hides under his blanket in the kennel but warms up slowly to kind, gentle people. Taco seems to love snuggling and being held, is learning to walk on a leash, and seems to like other small dogs. Let’s share this tiny angel and help him get out of the scary shelter and into a loving home. You can meet Taco in kennel # 4 at: Castaic Shelter, 31044 N.
